Assignment 7: Textures
Domenic Murtari (domenic.murtari@colorado.edu)

Appoximate Time to Complete: 5 hours

Controls: 
* 'p' to switch modes (projections)
* '0' snaps angles to 0,0
* arrows to rotate the world
* PgUp/PgDn zooms in/out
* +/- changes field of view of perspective
* 'l' toggles lighting
* m  toggles light movement
* [] lower/rise light